{"tid":1784484,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"幫人補習，學生係咪一定有回報？","createTime":"2019-12-15T16:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T10:38:28.000Z","uid":316420,"like":1,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b0fee9b40ac6d086d7d072c386b3769df35c83fe","tid":1784484,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:50:51.000Z","msg":"小弟有補習2個學生，都係中一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後term test 2個都分別有一科唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾功課佢地又唔做 叫佢地溫書又唔溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上堂係度挽發脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後2個星期前其中一個唔補<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家得番一樣小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢阿媽又要俾説話我聽 既然補左都唔合格 點解我要補<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s